Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:35.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:40.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:47.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:52.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.77,0:00:58.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever, I take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:06.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it’s not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:16.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:21.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard someone else’s biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.55,0:01:25.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn’t there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:30.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:36.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:42.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:48.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:52.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.79,0:01:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.02,0:01:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.84,0:02:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.28,0:02:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.27,0:02:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.44,0:02:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really intend to take him with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.70,0:02:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...do whatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.64,0:02:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take him by force!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.48,0:02:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only way to free him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.78,0:02:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Goodbye My Dear Underlings!\NFranky Departs"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put something on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.18,0:03:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You perv!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.10,0:03:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you destroy the town again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave town, you perv!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.23,0:03:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You good-for-nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me my swimsuit back, Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.40,0:03:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly! You think\Nyou can make me join you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just by stealing my swimsuit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:46.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,100)}"Nothing should phase men."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing should phase men.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:48.11,On Top - Copy,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,100)}"A man should be resourceful,\Neven with only the skin on his back."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.13,0:03:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man should be resourceful,\Neven with only the skin on his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.34,0:03:50.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2740,500)}"He should be like a lion that\Nstands against the waves!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should be like a lion that\Nstands against the waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.85,0:04:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He struck a pose, completely\Nexposing his private parts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the worst... He's the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.65,0:04:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I underestimated him!\NWhat a strong-willed guy he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a man among men!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just a total perv!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.95,0:04:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's okay to get rough\Nwith him, I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.06,0:04:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, Ice pops said that we\Nhad no choice but to take him by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.11,0:04:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dos Fleurs...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.64,0:04:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Hey, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.87,0:05:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You grabbed them! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're gonna crush them, Robin!\N--Ow, ow, ow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.81,0:05:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna come off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna be plucked off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like tangerines!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Robin! I want him to still\Nbe a man when he joins us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tear them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts just to watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?! Franky's in pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:06:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this gut-wrenching cry?!\NIt sounds like he's on the verge of death!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.18,0:06:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kinda feel sorry for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.14,0:06:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...even though he's a perv.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're telling us, pirates, to give up\Nthe treasure right in front of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can't back off unless\Nyou give us a good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I-I wanna stay on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I do appreciate you guys!\NIn fact, I can't thank you enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go with you and help you out,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's something I need to do here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I gave you the ship as a gift!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I'm not a shipwright\Nanymore in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that ship is the last ship I'll ever build!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.99,0:06:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my long-cherished desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.65,0:06:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That, indeed, is a dream ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, Franky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:07:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that ship has become\Nthe dream ship you're referring to yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Blueprints alone\Ncan't complete that ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After setting sail, it has to cross many seas
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and overcome many battles and hardships...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...before it reaches the end of the sea.\NAfter doing all those things,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then you can finally call it a dream ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when my best ship is completed one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll board that ship as a shipwright
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to witness that fated day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.84,0:07:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By that day, the ship will\Nprobably be falling apart,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm sure that it'll be\Ngiving off a magnificent light!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? Isn't that great, Tom-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you also become a sailor, you'll beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.19,0:07:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if your pirate blood is affecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:07:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! Moron-ky, someone like\Nyou can't surpass Tom-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.53,0:08:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, you Moron-ky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit, ribbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you're a man, do it resolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I wanna do has changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you wanna do? That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you're doing on\Nthis island right now is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...atonement.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.91,0:08:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still regretting that Tom-san\Nwas taken that day because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.02,0:08:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Tom-san had already\Nforgiven you on that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.93,0:08:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and tried to guide you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:09:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ships that would do something like that...\NThey're no longer my ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.64,0:09:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san... hit Franky for the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you do that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"They're no longer my ships," you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can say anything but that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with saying that?!\NI'm regretting it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.14,0:09:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only those ships didn't exist,\Nno one would have had to get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.01,0:09:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what kind of ship it is,\Nthe act of building it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is neither an act of good nor evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what kind of\Nships you choose to build,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.09,0:09:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but even if the ships you built hurt someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or even if they destroy the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at least the one who created\Nthem must love them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their creator mustn't deny them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.52,0:10:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame the ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man should be resolutely proud...\Nof the ships he created!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you brought the punks\Non the backstreets together...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you called yourself a bounty hunter\Nand protected this island from looters...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did all that to protect this\Ncity of water that Tom-san loved,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which was your way of atoning...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...though it doesn't appear that way to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.63,0:10:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not why I did what I did at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.46,0:10:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You quit building ships,\Nwhich was your favorite thing to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.06,0:10:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and have lived suppressing yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to live like that\Nfor the rest of your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Tom-san forgives you,\Nor even if I forgive you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.41,0:10:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nothing is gonna change, is it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it about time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for you to forgive yourself, Franky?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it about time for you to\Nstart living for your own dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has what you'll need for your journey, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the way, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Franky Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bro!\N--Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:12:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro! Please forgive us for all that\Nstuff we pulled! We're really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.33,0:12:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're prepared to receive\Nany kind of punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're fools, we racked what\Nlittle brains we have thinking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what did you rack what little\Nbrains you have thinking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How to steal my swimsuit? Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.47,0:12:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How to make me a pirate?!\NMind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.73,0:12:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my life! No one can decide it but me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I, your boss, willingly walk\Non the way paved by my underlings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's shameful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.38,0:12:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your brains are so small, then don't\Ntry to use them in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.01,0:12:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...aren't we even allowed to think a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.44,0:12:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're deeply indebted to you\Nfor taking in thugs like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we even allowed to\Nthink about your happiness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.06,0:13:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the fool here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.03,0:13:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--B-Bro!\N--Ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ow, ow, ow, ow...!\N--H-Hey, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go easy on him! Please!\NYou're gonna make him a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.96,0:13:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna come off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna be plucked off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like grapes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, grapes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Nico Robin!\NYou're not gonna get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna come off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna be plucked off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.15,0:13:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like apples!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.61,0:13:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... pples...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My tears won't stop because of the pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:14:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh? You aren't doing anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only did it once, the very first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How sly of him to pretend\Nthat he's crying out of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?\N--Just once?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Ow, ow, ow, ow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.16,0:14:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts so bad I can't stop the tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.08,0:14:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't found them yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them get away no matter what!\NLook far and wide for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.51,0:15:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts! It hurts! I can't stop the tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.90,0:15:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I be okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen you around.\NWhat's with you, bikini guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so stuck-up on these backstreets.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.51,0:15:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh... What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.59,0:15:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you mock us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite strong. You're just\Nwasting that strength by being a thug.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.38,0:16:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zambai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Franky. I've decided to make the\Nbackstreets of Water Seven my turf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.95,0:16:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice meeting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.02,0:16:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.96,0:16:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.36,0:16:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm feeling great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to one more bar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you over there with the stylish bikini!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.03,0:16:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a drink together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take you to a bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You young girls, don't sponge booze\Nfrom others in broad daylight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know a place that serves good cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.85,0:16:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.79,0:17:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro! Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.91,0:17:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Give me something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.95,0:17:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring everyone who has nothing to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.11,0:17:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go as nuts as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're starting the Franky Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's our start!\N--It's our start!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We're the Franky Family!\N--We're the Franky Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.76,0:17:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky! Franky! Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.87,0:17:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky! Franky! Franky!...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.25,0:18:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you... live without me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.18,0:18:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The face of the Water Seven underworld...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll work together to take\Nover that role splendidly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.73,0:18:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.67,0:18:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how far you go,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're your underlings for the rest of our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.40,0:18:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop the tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.52,0:18:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.78,0:18:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Zoro! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.24,0:18:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your grandpa is back, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're at the opposite seashore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.35,0:18:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're looking for us now!\NThey're going to attack us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.08,0:19:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Why?! I thought he said\Nhe wasn't gonna capture us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.67,0:19:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would we know?!\NHurry up and get ready to set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.40,0:19:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky! You still haven't\Nput on your swimsuit yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.03,0:19:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm giving this back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.17,0:19:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come on board, Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.34,0:19:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Board my ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so cocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are total amateurs who\Ncould only manage makeshift repairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.78,0:19:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a pity for such a magnificent ship\Nnot to have a shipwright on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I don't have much choice\Nbut to help you guys out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Franky, will be the shipwright on your ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! We've got a new crew member!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.68,0:19:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry! Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat is a man we can trust!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.64,0:20:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san... I'm leaving this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, teach me how to draw\Nblueprints for a pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.17,0:20:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to bed yet, Tom-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.93,0:20:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm... It's this island's hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't a good disciple. I always\Ncaused you nothing but trouble, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you guys hear about the scrap heap island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom's Workers has finished\Nbuilding the sea train, you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:21:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.12,0:21:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Galley-La's foremen...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.48,0:21:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take good care of Iceberg!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.16,0:21:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've caused you nothing\Nbut trouble, too, Iceberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.85,0:21:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old hag Kokoro, little one and bunny...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.66,0:21:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ribbit...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.00,0:21:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yokozuna...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.51,0:21:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perv!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.49,0:21:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Lively townspeople...\N--Where're you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming back, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My little sisters...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.10,0:21:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sodom... Gomorrah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.46,0:21:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... my dear underlings...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.52,0:22:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm stepping out for a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.19,0:22:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put on your swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.16,0:22:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Usopp's coming back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.38,0:22:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.05,0:22:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then! Let's go get him right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.10,0:22:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.28,0:22:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?\N--I won't allow any of us to go get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.98,0:22:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.65,0:22:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Departing the City of Water!\NUsopp Mans Up and Brings Closure to the Duel!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.75,0:22:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
